<h2 style="margin-top: 0; text-align: center;">More documentation</h2>

<CardGrid>
  <Card title="Help Center for ArchivesSpace members" icon="star">
    The <a
      href="https://archivesspace.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/ADC/pages/917045261/ArchivesSpace+Help+Center"
      >ArchivesSpace Help Center</a
    > contains the user manual, tutorial videos, and recordings of past trainings.
    Help Center access is a <a
      href="https://archivesspace.org/membership/member-benefits"
      >benefit of ArchivesSpace membership</a
    > and requires a member login.
  </Card>
  <Card title="API reference" icon="list-format">
    ArchivesSpace <a href="https://archivesspace.github.io/archivesspace/api/"
      >REST API reference</a
    > that documents the endpoints used by the backend server to edit records in
    the application.
  </Card>
  <Card title="Yard docs" icon="open-book">
    Ruby <a href="https://archivesspace.github.io/archivesspace/doc/"
      >Yard-generated documentation</a
    > for the ArchivesSpace codebase.
  </Card>
</CardGrid>

<style>
  .hero {
    display: grid;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 1rem;
    padding-bottom: 1rem;

    img {
      object-fit: contain;
      width: 70px;
      height: auto;
      margin-inline: auto;
    }

    h1 {
      max-width: 400px;
      margin: 0 !important;
      margin-inline: auto;
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .hero__blurb {
      margin-top: 0;
      margin-inline: auto;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;

      p {
        margin-top: 0.5rem;
        font-size: 1.1rem;

        &:first-child {
          margin-top: 0;
        }
      }
    }
  }

  @media (min-width: 600px) {
    .hero {
      gap: 1.5rem;

      img {
        width: 80px;
      }

      h1 {
        max-width: 100%;
        font-size: 1.75rem;
      }

      .hero__blurb {
        p {
          margin-top: 1rem;
          font-size: 1.25rem;
        }
      }
    }
  }

  @media (min-width: 60rem) {
    .hero {
      gap: 2rem;

      img {
        width: 115px;
      }

      h1 {
        max-width: 100%;
        font-size: 1.875rem;
      }

      .hero__blurb {
        p {
          font-size: 1.3rem;
        }
      }
    }
  }

  @media (min-width: 72rem) {
    .hero {
      grid-template-columns: 4fr 8fr;
      grid-template-rows: auto auto;
      column-gap: 3rem;
      row-gap: 1rem;
      padding-block: clamp(2.5rem, calc(1rem + 10vmin), 10rem);
      padding-right: 1rem;
      padding-left: 1rem;

      img {
        grid-column: 1;
        grid-row: 1 / span 2;
        align-self: center;
        width: min(100%, 25rem);
      }

      h1 {
        font-size: 2.5rem;
        text-align: start;
      }

      .hero__blurb {
        margin: 0;
      }
    }
  }
</style>
